"savedLayouts"
Object - Each property is the name of the layout with the value being an Array of objects with the following schema:

    layoutName : widgets
    
    "layoutName"
    String - User defined name of the layout
    "widgets"
    Array - Contains configuration information on widgets used in its layout
        
        "name": String - name of the widget (look up in registeredWidgets to get filepath)
        "x": Integer - X coordinate of the browser window
        "y": Integer - Y coordinate of the browser window
        "width": Integer - width of the browser window
        "height": Integer - height of the browser window

"currentLayout"
String - Name of the currently loaded layout

"registeredWidgets"
Object - Each property is the user given name of a widget containing the path to its respective HTML file
